import Header from '../components/header'; import { useSelector } from 'react-redux'; import { RootState } from '../redux/store'; import { DebtData } from '../utils/type'; import { MDBContainer, MDBRow, MDBCard, MDBCol, MDBBadge, MDBCardBody, MDBBtn, MDBIcon, MDBCardFooter } from 'mdb-react-ui-kit'; import dashboard1 from '../images/dashboard1.svg'; import dashboard2 from '../images/dashboard2.svg'; function DashboardPage() { const { debtData } = useSelector((state: RootState) => state.debtList); const totalDebtAmount = debtData.reduce((total, debt) => total + debt.debtAmount, 0); const formatter = new Intl.NumberFormat('tr-TR', { style: 'currency', currency: 'TRY', }); const averageInstallment = debtData.reduce((total, debt) => total + debt.installment, 0) / debtData.length; const totalInterestRate = debtData.reduce((total, debt) => total + debt.interestRate, 0) / debtData.length; // Ortalama faiz oran覺n覺 hesaplama const averageInterestRate = totalInterestRate; return (
DashboardPage

Total debt

{formatter.format(totalDebtAmount)}

Average Installment

{averageInstallment}

Average Interest Rate

24.57%

); } export default DashboardPage;
